Middle East & Africa: Emerging New Markets
In the Middle East and Africa, the market is at an emerging stage. Increased consumer awareness and access to international beauty brands are anticipated to boost demand. The trend of luxury personal care, coupled with a growing middle-class population, signals promising opportunities for stakeholders in this geographical locale.

